WEBVTT

00:00:00.660 --> 00:00:03.560
Maya, I don't know what I would
have done without your help.

00:00:04.199 --> 00:00:07.366
It was my responsibility to
guide you through these conflicts.

00:00:07.391 --> 00:00:09.753
We've all faced them at some point.

00:00:10.110 --> 00:00:13.003
Now let's see whether you've
arrived at the right conclusions.